on Kultur oder auf Aspekte medizinischer Kommunikation reicht.  aThis volume brings together central works by Susanne Günthner that reflect that breadth of her years-long research, including an analysis of the grammatical structures of interactional language and a description of linguistic patterns in communicative practices and genres, as well as anthropological linguistic studies on doing gender and analyses of the communicative construction of culture and medical communication.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 4aAnthropologische Linguistik. 4aInteraktionale Linguistik. 4aKonversationsanalyse. 4aProsodieforschung. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh  aAnthropological Linguistics.  aConversation Analysis.  aInteractional Linguistics.  aProsody Research.1 aFladrich, Marcel, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFladrich, Marcel, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aGünthner, Susanne, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aImo, Wolfgang, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aImo, Wolfgang, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aKönig, Katharina, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKönig, Katharina, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aLanwer, Jens Philipp, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLanwer, Jens Philipp, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aWeidner, Beate, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWeidner, Beate, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabular